items.title: LD Compatible Toner to Replace Dell 331-8431 (XKGFP) Extra High Yield Magenta Toner Cartridge for Dell C3760 and C3765
items.description: This is a compatible replacement laser toner cartridge to replace the Dell 331-8431 (XKGFP) extra high yield magenta cartridge. It is guaranteed to perform with your Dell laser printer and replaces the high yield 331-8427 and standard yield 331-8423 cartridges. These compatible alternatives to the Dell 331-8431 cartridges are manufactured 100% brand new by a manufacturer that is not endorsed or associated with Dell and are guaranteed by LDProducts.com to work with your Dell printer. Our compatible alternatives for OEM 331-8431 / XKGFP laser toner cartridges and supplies are manufactured to the highest performance and quality standards and will deliver optimal prints. Our compatible laser toners are an economical alternative to expensive OEM XKGFP Dell laser toners  and offer big savings over brand-name 331-8431 laser toner cartridges and supplies.
